^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|So, on this original hand Boater has a minimum with 3-card support, and answers choice b) by bidding 3@H. For Bonnie it is close between pass and 4H. Using Bergen, she has 8 HCP. Subtract 1 for @SQ singleton. Subtract 1 for 3 quacks and no A or 10 for a total of 6.|
